name: WERKSCHAU WIESBADEN BAG
description:
That’s the bag I designed for the graduation exhibition »Werkschau Wiesbaden«. We produced only a small silkscreen collection, but there are a few left. You will get one bag plus one button (Printed in Pantone) for 5 euros (plus shipping). 
Contact me, if you want to buy more items to calculate the costs. :)
